A woman identified as Mama Daba, has been arrested for pouring hot water on her neighbour, Mama Boma. According to reports, the two women were having a misunderstanding, yesterday, at their Mile 1, PortHarcourt residence in Rivers State, when Mama Boma was scalded with hot water. The suspect, who allegedly has a history of assaulting her neighbours, was subsequently apprehended and handed over to the police.